content: The destination already contains files and folders with the same name.

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message when a user attempts to add files or folders to a destination that already contains items with the same name. It appears in a conflict resolution dialog box, indicating that an overwrite option may be available.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'コピー先に同じ名前のファイルとフォルダが既に存在します。' is a literal translation, but could be more natural in Japanese. A more common and user-friendly phrasing would be 'コピー先に同じ名前のファイルやフォルダがあります。'
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: コピー先に同じ名前のファイルやフォルダがあります。

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation '목표에 이미 같은 이름의 파일과 폴더가 있습니다.' while understandable, is not the most natural phrasing. '목표' (goal/target) isn't the best choice for 'destination' in this context. It implies a final goal, rather than a location.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 대상 위치에 이미 같은 이름의 파일과 폴더가 있습니다.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Lao translation 'ຈຸດຫມາຍປັດຈຸບັນມີແລ້ວບັນຈຸເອກະສານແລະໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນ' is a literal translation but sounds awkward. A more natural phrasing might be 'ຈຸດໝາຍປ້າຍນີ້ມີເອກະສານ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນຢູ່ແລ້ວ' or 'ມີເອກະສານ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນຢູ່ແລ້ວໃນຈຸດໝາຍປ້າຍນີ້'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ຈຸດຫມາຍປ້າຍນີ້ມີເອກະສານ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນຢູ່ແລ້ວ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The use of 'ແລະ' twice is a bit clunky. Combining 'ເອກະສານແລະໂຟນເດີ' into a single term might be preferable in a more formal context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ຈຸດຫມາຍປ້າຍນີ້ມີເອກະສານແລະໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນຢູ່ແລ້ວ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ෆෝල්ඩර' (folder) is misspelled. The correct spelling is 'ෆෝල්ඩර්'.

The word 'фолдере' is a slightly awkward wording. While technically correct, 'фасцикле' or 'чаршије' might be more natural in this context, depending on the intended tone. 'Фолдре' is acceptable, but potentially not ideal for a more formal tone.
